description:
This week on Unqualified Anna and Sim sit down with the insanely hilarious Kaitlin Olson (It’s Always Sunny, The Mick) and Scott MacArthur (The Mick)! The gang reminisces about college, dating now vs. the past, human evolution and what it’s like to work on multiple shows at once! After playing How Would You Proceed, Deal Breakers and Obscure Parenting Trivia they call Kate, who’s not sure what to do when someone she has a past with won’t stop reaching out even after proposing to his girlfriend, and Lindsey, who wants to know if she and her boyfriend are crossing the lines of comfort! Oh boy, it's a good one.

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
